attributes.description: This dashboard shows CSPM logs collected by the Sysdig integration.

params.markdown:
This dashboard provides an overview of the CSPM logs collected by the Sysdig integration.

The dashboard provides metrics for requirements evaluated, including passing and failing requirements. It also showcases a policy overview table displaying failing requirements, available control fixes, resource violations by severity, and accepted risks. The requirements table offers an overview of failing controls, accepted risks, passing resources, and more.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/sysdig/overview)
